{"type":"message","id":"27662914","parentId":"b88660e1","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:44:38.143Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"你能做什么？\" (What can you do?) in Chinese. This is a common question about my capabilities. I need to respond in Chinese since the user is speaking Chinese and we're in a DingTalk group chat environment.\n\nLet me check my context:\n- I'm in a group chat \"杭州余杭钛酷贸易中心\" with user \"魏新波\"\n- This is a group chat, so I should follow the group chat guidelines from AGENTS.md\n- I should be smart about when to speak - respond when directly addressed or can add clear value\n- This is a direct question addressed to me, so I should respond\n- I should write like a human and avoid overly formal language\n\nI should explain what I can do in a helpful, concise way. Since this is a group chat and the user is asking about my capabilities, I should give a brief overview of what I can help with.\n\nI don't need to read any files for this basic question - it's about my capabilities which are defined by the system. I should respond naturally in Chinese.\n\nLet me craft a response that:\n1. Answers the question clearly\n2. Is concise and human-like\n3. Fits the group chat context (not too formal, not too robotic)\n4. Shows I'm helpful and capable\n\nI'll respond in Chinese about what I can do based on my OpenClaw capabilities.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是你的 AI 助手，生活在 OpenClaw 系统里。我能做的事很多，比如：\n\n- 读写和管理文件，帮你整理资料、备份数据\n- 执行命令行操作，自动化重复任务\n- 管理日历、提醒事项、待办清单\n- 搜索网络、获取天气、查汇率\n- 生成和优化代码\n- 在 Telegram/WhatsApp/DingTalk 等平台收发消息\n- 控制家居设备、监控摄像头\n- 写日报、周报、总结文档\n- 使用各种技能（比如天气查询、健康检查、Oracle 提示工程等）\n\n如果你有具体想做的事，直接告诉我就行，我会看看怎么帮你搞定。\n\n（对了，我还能帮你设置定时任务，比如每天早上 9 点自动 check 你的日历和邮件，有重要的事我会主动找你。）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":9358,"output":802,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10160,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773233071178}}
