{"type":"message","id":"a93fcdab","parentId":"82c6d9fe","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:16:09.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提到了\"agent-browser\"，这可能是某个特定的技能或工具名称。让我搜索一下系统中是否存在这个技能或可执行文件。\n\n首先，让我检查 openclaw 的技能列表，看看有没有叫 \"agent-browser\" 或类似名称的技能。我注意到之前列出的技能中并没有这个。但用户特意提到，可能是：\n\n1. 一个尚未列出的技能\n2. 一个独立的 CLI 工具\n3. 一个需要安装的第三方工具\n4. 或者用户记错了名字\n\n让我先尝试搜索一下是否有任何与浏览器相关的工具或技能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"让我找找有没有 `agent-browser` 这个工具或技能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3cead016aa9640fe883a0d93","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which agent-browser browser-browse browser 2>/dev/null || echo \"not in PATH\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":21217,"output":371,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21588,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773238563499}}
