{"type":"message","id":"a65f8dd6","parentId":"dd50300d","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:23:54.084Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我推荐钢丝跳绳。这是一个正常的购物建议请求，不涉及任何违规内容。我需要：\n1. 理解需求：小朋友身高1米28，跳绳速度1分钟209个，想换绳子提升速度\n2. 价格范围：20-100元\n3. 需要从品牌、销量、评价、性价比、功能等角度推荐\n\n我可以使用 agent-browser 去搜索一下市面上的钢丝跳绳产品，获取真实的品牌、价格、评价信息。\n\n让我先搜索一下，然后给出推荐。\n\n需要搜索的关键词：钢丝跳绳、儿童跳绳、速度跳绳等。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你选一款适合小朋友的钢丝跳绳。先搜索一下市面上的热门产品，从品牌、销量、评价、性价比等角度分析。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2283d5cd8f7c429ca23704ec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/root/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/bin/agent-browser open \"https://search.jd.com/Search?keyword=钢丝跳绳+儿童+速度&enc=utf-8\" && sleep 4 && /root/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/bin/agent-browser snapshot --compact | head -n 80","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":46165,"output":455,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46620,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773242625188}}
