{"type":"message","id":"86cd5131","parentId":"75e7b28d","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:30:04.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"淘宝和京东都需要登录，无法直接访问商品详情。让我尝试一些其他平台：\n- 拼多多？可能也需要登录\n- 小红书商城？可能不需要\n- 网易严选？可能需要\n- 或者一些评测网站，他们会有购买链接\n\n让我试试看小红书或者B站的文章，这些平台的内容通常不需要登录就能看，而且带货文章里会有购买链接。\n\n搜索：\"儿童钢丝跳绳推荐\" 可能找到一些评测文章。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"电商平台都需要登录。让我试试一些不需要登录就能访问的评测文章或导购网站："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6c1a83a9cd434aa0b752d142","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/root/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/bin/agent-browser open \"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/684578321\" && sleep 4 && /root/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/bin/agent-browser snapshot -c | head -n 100","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":51384,"output":379,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51763,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773242999597}}
