{"type":"message","id":"baa8c47d","parentId":"2d8b5ee6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:39:35.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户给了一个淘宝链接，让我分析这款产品。链接是：https://e.tb.cn/h.i3tDEk2XQGRsNaM?tk=nYwVUEHwTSg HU926\n\n这个链接看起来是淘宝的分享链接。我需要用 agent-browser 打开这个链接，然后获取商品信息、价格、评价等数据。\n\n让我尝试打开这个页面。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"收到了，我来抓取这个淘宝商品页面的信息并分析。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ad239d6cd80d462d9f9c3742","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/root/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/bin/agent-browser open \"https://e.tb.cn/h.i3tDEk2XQGRsNaM?tk=nYwVUEHwTSg\" && sleep 5 && /root/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/bin/agent-browser snapshot -c | head -n 80","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":54976,"output":318,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55294,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773243569788}}
